{
  "stem": "54.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody grab a-- a little-- just a little piece, you know, just to feel like that-- that you have something in your mouth.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was going on-- that's it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't see him anymore, because they probably-- maybe they caught him that time, or they told him not to do it, because otherwise they're going to kill him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was-- unfortunate, we were not long-- this was our luck, that we were not long in Auschwitz in camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Only two months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They tortured us for two months like that-- every single morning, kneel on snow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we were standing already a few times in line to get our numbers, the tattoos.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were too busy, they had too many people coming from Lodz that time, because they were liquidating the whole ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were a lot of people coming there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they didn't do the-- the tattoos for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they decided to send us from there to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Bergen-Belsen, it was bad, but not as bad as in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came into a bunk-- into a bungalow, where we were sleeping on the straw, straw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only straw-- we didn't have any mattresses, nothing to cover up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to sleep in clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was a bungalow left from soldiers was-- were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The German soldiers were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The straw had a lot of fleas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't sleep at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on the wall from that bungalow was in the thousands of thousands names on the wall are written.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You were standing and looking at the wall, it was one name after the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Thousands of names were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we thought, maybe we'd find somebody from our people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
